In the INTEREST OF: M.F.G. and Z.F.G.; Respondents, Juvenile Officer, Respondent,
v.
M.B., Appellant. WD 81312 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. ORDER FILED: January 15, 2019 David Suroff, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Appellant. Erica McCabe, Kansas City, MO, Co-Counsel for Appellant. Ryan Kaiser, Kansas City, MO, Counsel for Respondent, Juvenile Officer. Elizabeth Walker, Kansas City, MO, Co-Counsel for Respondent, Juvenile Officer. Anika Hickman, Kansas City, MO, Counsel and Guardian Ad Litem for Respondents. Claire Terrebonne, Kansas City, MO, Co-Counsel and Guardian Ad Litem for Respondents. Before Division Two: Alok Ahuja, P.J., Thomas H. Newton, and Mark D. Pfeiffer, JJ.

ORDER

Per Curiam:

Mr. Michael Burns appeals a finding of neglect by the Jackson County Circuit Court under section 211.031, R.S.Mo. (2016). For reasons stated in the memorandum provided to the parties, we affirm. Rule 84.16(b).
